                          </span>


                        </li>
                    <li>OR The server encountered a problem, please try again later</li>
                </ul>

            </h2>

        </div>


        <div class="card-footer"> For more information, please contact us at &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            <a href="mailto:{{ webMasterMail }}">
                <span class='badge  badge-danger'>{{ webMasterMail }}</span></a>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;

        </div>

    </div>

{% endblock %}